Regional School Unit 60 is looking for a Soccer coach to join our program. Apply now.

Qualifications:
Experience Preferred;
Strong communication skills;
Ability to communicate effectively with players, parents, community members, and the athletic director
Commitment to the program as an integral part of the district school program;
Ability to grasp and understand student body funds;
Ability to relate effectively with colleagues, and maintain an active association with the professional coaching community.
Terms of Employment:
Starting Date:  ASAP
Salary:       $3379-$4858 DOE 2025-2026 Coaching Salary Schedule

